{"lemma":"مُباهَلَةٌ","slug":"مُباهَلَةٌ","root":"ب.ه.ل","root_slug":"ب-ه-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ه-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3437"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3437","headword_ar":"مُبَاهَلَةٌ","root":"bhl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of cursing each other:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb:) inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAhlhu","text_ar":"باهلهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cursed him, being cursed by him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [or rather]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAhalotuhu","text_ar":"بَاهَلْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I joined with him in imprecating the curse of God upon whichever of us did wrong."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) Hence the saying of Ibn-Mes'ood,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano $aA='a","text_ar":"مَنْ شَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAhalotuhu A^an~a suwrapa AlquSoraY nazalato baEoda Albaqarapi","text_ar":"بَاهَلْتُهُ اَنَّ سُورَةَ القُصْرَى نَزَلَتْ بَعْدَ البَقَرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whosoever will, I will contend with him by imprecating the curse of God upon whichever of us is wrong, that the shorter chapter of “Women” came down"},{"kind":"text","text":"from heaven"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after"},{"kind":"text","text":"the chapter of “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Cow”"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, accord. to one recital, he said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA Eanotuhu","text_ar":"لَا عَنْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": for when they differed respecting a thing, they used to come together, and say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hi EalaY","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهِ عَلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baholapu","text_ar":"بَهْلَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~aAlimi min~aA","text_ar":"الظَّالِمِ مِنَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The curse of God be upon such of us as is the wrongdoer!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAhl baEoDuhumo","text_ar":"باهل بَعْضُهُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoDFA","text_ar":"بَعْضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tb~hlwA","text_ar":"تبّهلوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbAhlwA","text_ar":"تباهلوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"all signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They cursed one another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they joined in imprecating a curse upon such of them as was the wrongdoer:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbthlwA","text_ar":"ابتهلوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the like: whence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a nabotahilo","text_ar":"ثُمَّ نَبْتَهِلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [iii. 54], (Bd, TA,) as some explain it, (TA,) meaning ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a natabaAhalo","text_ar":"ثُمَّ نَتَبَاهَلْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then let us imprecate a curse upon such of us as is the liar."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd. [But see also 8 below.])"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","Bd"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}